Paper: hep-th/0212326

Date: 2002-12-29

Title: Classical Geometry of De Sitter Spacetime

Authors: Yoonbai Kim, Chae Young Oh, Namil Park (Sungkyunkwan U.)

Comments: 40 pages, 12 figures (ps or eps)

Classical geometry of de Sitter spacetime is reviewed in arbitrarydimensions. Topics include coordinate systems, geodesic motions, and Penrosediagrams with detailed calculations.